highlights.text: Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #9.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 926 days straight.
“Medida Protetiva - Ao Vivo” by João Bosco & Vinícius and Gusttavo Lima is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #105.
“Duvido - Ao Vivo” by Turma do Pagode, Ferrugem, and Mumuzinho is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 79 spots at #96.
